feat(frontend): initialize Next.js 14+ app with Jake's UX

- Set up Next.js 14+ with App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- Configure western-themed color palette (saloon, dusty)
- Install core dependencies: Framer Motion, Rive, Howler.js, Radix UI

Core Components Built:
- JakeCharacter: Rive state machine integration (10 states)
- JakeVoice: Audio player with waveform visualization
- CameraCapture: Multi-photo capture with <500KB compression
- ResearchAnimation: 3-stage signature animation (looking/researching/deciding)
- OfferCard: Offer display with market context

Pages Implemented:
- Landing page: Hero with Jake, How It Works, FAQ
- Submit page: Camera/upload flow with compression
- Offer page: Research animation + offer display

Infrastructure:
- API client wrapper for backend integration
- WebSocket hook for real-time updates
- Camera hook with MediaDevices API
- Jake personality scripts and character states
- Utility functions (compression, formatting)

Additional:
- Jake research choreography utilities
- Admin login page component
- Input/Label UI components

Next: Registration flow, Dashboard, Batch mode, PWA config

